

---

## 1. Power Connections

| ESP32 Pin | Connection |
|----------|------------|
| VIN / 5V | 5V Power Supply / Battery Regulator |
| 3V3 | 3.3V Rail (Sensors & Modules) |
| GND | Common Ground (All Components) |

‚ö†Ô∏è **All components share a common ground**

---

## 2. OLED Display (1.3 inch, I2C)

| OLED Pin | ESP32 Pin |
|---------|-----------|
| VCC | 3V3 |
| GND | GND |
| SDA | GPIO 21 |
| SCL | GPIO 22 |

- Communication Protocol: **I2C**
- Controller: SSD1306 / SH1106

---

## 3. MAX30100 Pulse Oximeter (I2C)

| MAX30100 Pin | ESP32 Pin |
|--------------|-----------|
| VCC | 3V3 |
| GND | GND |
| SDA | GPIO 21 |
| SCL | GPIO 22 |
| INT | GPIO 19 (Optional) |

- Shares I2C bus with OLED

---

## 4. nRF24L01 Wireless Module (SPI ‚Äì 3.3V ONLY)

‚ö†Ô∏è **Do NOT connect nRF24L01 to 5V**

| nRF24L01 Pin | ESP32 Pin |
|--------------|-----------|
| VCC | 3V3 |
| GND | GND |
| CE | GPIO 4 |
| CSN | GPIO 5 |
| SCK | GPIO 18 |
| MOSI | GPIO 23 |
| MISO | GPIO 19 |

üìå Recommended: 10¬µF + 0.1¬µF capacitor across VCC‚ÄìGND

---

## 5. LM35 Temperature Sensor

| LM35 Pin | ESP32 Pin |
|---------|-----------|
| VCC | 3V3 |
| OUT | GPIO 34 (ADC) |
| GND | GND |

- GPIO 34 is ADC-only and ideal for analog sensing

---

## 6. Vibration Sensor Module

| Vibration Sensor Pin | ESP32 Pin |
|--------------------|-----------|
| VCC | 3V3 |
| GND | GND |
| DO (Digital Output) | GPIO 35 |

---

## 7. Piezoelectric Sensors (Bioacoustic Sensing)

| Piezo Sensor | ESP32 Pin |
|-------------|-----------|
| Piezo 1 | GPIO 32 (ADC) |
| Piezo 2 | GPIO 33 (ADC) |
| Piezo 3 | GPIO 36 (ADC) |
| Other Terminal | GND |

üìå Use high-value resistor (‚âà1 MŒ©) and protection diode for ADC safety

---

## 8. LED Indicator

| LED Pin | ESP32 Pin |
|--------|-----------|
| Anode (+) | GPIO 2 |
| Cathode (‚Äì) | GND (via 220Œ© resistor) |

- GPIO 2 often has onboard LED

---

## 9. Buzzer (Alert System)

| Buzzer Pin | ESP32 Pin |
|-----------|-----------|
| Positive (+) | GPIO 27 |
| Negative (‚Äì) | GND |

- Active buzzer recommended for simplicity

---

## 10. Summary of Interfaces

| Interface | ESP32 Pins Used |
|---------|----------------|
| I2C | GPIO 21, GPIO 22 |
| SPI | GPIO 18, 19, 23, 5, 4 |
| ADC | GPIO 32, 33, 34, 35, 36 |
| Digital Output | GPIO 2, GPIO 27 |


